Package: novelCoViD
Type: Package
Title: CoViD-19 data visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: c(person("Rasa", "Ashrafi", email = "rasa.ashrafi@gmail.com", role = c("cre","aut")))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <rasa.ashrafi@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows users to obtain live worldwide data from the novel CoronaVirus Disease (CoViD-19) published by the Johns Hopkins University. The package provides basic map and plot functions to explore the dataset.
